{"tid":1463039,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知大家點睇 有個關於黑警扮記者嘅陰謀論","createTime":"2019-08-13T11:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T12:22:42.000Z","uid":259786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6fb8f20367e21f7ab0f9ee3bab255af114cacaed","tid":1463039,"uid":259786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:56:40.000Z","msg":"P牌仔 但係好在意一件事 想大家關注下<br />\n早前睇度個post 關於黑警 劉勝華輔警現身機場同示威現場扮記者<br />\n其實自己第一次見到有關相片應該喺金水個facebook post <br />\n但係就有好多爭論話佢到底係唔係警察 <br />\n又有人話係保鑣 保護記者 <br />\n唔想炒車所以就冇跟進落去<br />\n<br />\n之後琴日又有post 話見到佢喺機場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1459377\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1459377</a><br />\n而見到唔少言論話佢係藍屍<br />\n當中我好在意呢個screenshot對話  （參考原post）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gdqhkpc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgdqhkpc.jpg&h=a0dc0015&s={SIZE}\" /> 或者原post人可以交代下<br />\n&ldquo;我在鏡頭後工作&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/351910878\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F351910878&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2BjJoBOSHi9wRld7hxL8G3jc%3D&h=6417390e\" target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/351910878</a><br />\n追查Stuart Ramsay 同 Michael Herd 係Sky嘅記者<br />\n但係睇完條片覺得完全是描寫示威者為暴徒<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ramsaysky?lang=en \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Framsaysky%3Flang%3Den%20&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2BjJoBOSHi9wRld7hxL8G3jc%3D&h=6f315fd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ramsaysky?lang=en </a><br />\n奇怪係Stuart Ramsay 本人冇喺twitter上講自己喺香港 完全神秘<br />\n<br />\n而條片有同條友facebook 傳嘅一樣 佢一直都幫警察拍緊野<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/alain.lau.7/videos/10219915554587417/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Falain.lau.7%2Fvideos%2F10219915554587417%2F&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2BjJoBOSHi9wRld7hxL8G3jc%3D&h=0cbf02ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/alain.lau.7/videos/10219915554587417/</a><br />\n<br />\n各位可以參考<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VmdPA6ZdQwQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVmdPA6ZdQwQ&d=2QIn9Yr%2BOYfG2lc2ZV7v%2BjJoBOSHi9wRld7hxL8G3jc%3D&h=961b3978\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VmdPA6ZdQwQ</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">就算佢宜家唔係現職警察 但真係輔警 即係同警察有聯絡 </span><br />\n<br />\n今日都有出post話個輔警又出現<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1461397/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1461397/</a><br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得好奇怪<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如果佢真係&ldquo;保鑣&rdquo; 只係保護記者<br />\n乜野記者 邊間報社會出咁多錢 請保鑣啊？</strong></span><br />\n而且點解次次提到佢 就會咁多人出黎幫佢澄清？？？<br />\n又唔見其他搵到嘅仔有人幫佢哋澄清？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n仲係次次都係佢 而身為藍屍嘅佢 又點會保護記者啊</span><br />\n定係趁住記者拍野 佢自己拍埋啊？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pyqhkrc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPyqhkrc.png&h=ce87085d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vJVdDcT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvJVdDcT.png&h=adc44e69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係會唔會警方請外國人去採訪因為我地對佢地信任度高<br />\n<strong>咁呢個劉勝華唔係扮記者 而係&ldquo;真&rdquo;記者連同兩個外國人去拍攝示威者。</strong><br />\n鬼之佢地拍埋 剪埋啲片 以後會用黎做乜<br />\n（大膽假設 如果以後有獨立調查 佢地拍呢d片全部都會用黎抹黑示威者）<br />\n唔係搞分化 唔係搞分化 唔係搞分化<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">難分真與假<br />\n唔想炒車 <br />\n但係值得關注 </span></span><br />\n或者以後喺現場見到 劉輔警 可以去問候下 say 個hi <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /